ActDepartment of Foreign Affairs, Trade and Development Act
SubjectCanada-Atlantic Provinces Agreement on International Business Development
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of Foreign Affairs to enter into the Canada-Atlantic Provinces AGREEMENT on INTERNATIONAL BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT with the governments of NOVA SCOTIA, NEW BRUNSWICK, PRINCE EDWARD ISLAND AND NEWFOUNDLAND AND LABRADOR, for a period of one year, commencing upon final signature of all parties.
